Title : Bob Magness
Text : '''Bob Magness''' (June 3, 1924 &ndash; November 15, 1996)<ref>http://www.cablecenter.org/barco-library-hauser-oral-history/item/magness-bob.html</ref><ref>http://www.bizjournals.com/denver/stories/1996/11/25/editorial1.html</ref> was an American businessman who founded [[Tele-Communications Inc.|Tele-Communications, Inc (TCI)]].  

At the time of his death, TCI was the largest [[cable television]] provider in the United States, and [[Forbes Magazine]] listed Magness as a billionaire and the second-richest businessman in [[Colorado]]. <ref>http://articles.latimes.com/1996-11-18/business/fi-351_1_bob-magness</ref>

